title: Publishers Weekly. 8 November 2010.
description:
Publishers Weekly. 8 November 2010.

Publishers Weekly is the definitive professional resource 
covering every aspect of book publishing and book selling. 
Over 20,000 book and media professionals turn to Publishers 
Weekly each week for news and information. Publishers Weekly 
covers the creation, production, marketing and sale of 
the written word in book, audio, video and electronic formats.

Enjoy.
